1
00:00:13,040 --> 00:00:14,600
How dare you show up here.

2
00:00:17,240 --> 00:00:18,880
None of you will leave here today.

3
00:00:18,880 --> 00:00:20,560
His Majesty has arrived!

4
00:00:23,200 --> 00:00:24,660
Greetings, Your Majesty.

5
00:00:26,760 --> 00:00:28,220
Greetings, Your Majesty.

6
00:00:32,960 --> 00:00:34,560
Why does he have the mask?

7
00:00:37,760 --> 00:00:40,090
Your Majesty, what is the meaning of this?

8
00:00:40,200 --> 00:00:41,860
Well, my beloved Minister Su,

9
00:00:42,080 --> 00:00:43,480
I am here to ask you

10
00:00:43,760 --> 00:00:46,760
why you wanted to assassinate the foreign envoy.

11
00:00:48,720 --> 00:00:50,980
Your Majesty, where does this come from?

12
00:00:52,200 --> 00:00:55,520
Your Majesty, he ordered us to assassinate the envoy.

13
00:00:57,800 --> 00:00:58,720
Your Majesty.

14
00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:00,440
I have just been entrusted with an important task.

15
00:01:00,440 --> 00:01:02,400
It is exactly the time for me to serve the Great Jin.

16
00:01:02,400 --> 00:01:04,560
Assassinating the envoy brings me no benefit at all.

17
00:01:04,560 --> 00:01:05,560
This is slander.

18
00:01:06,920 --> 00:01:08,440
Stop quibbling.

19
00:01:09,360 --> 00:01:12,039
This folding fan pendant you left at the scene

20
00:01:12,720 --> 00:01:15,680
is the ironclad proof of your collusion with foreign countries

21
00:01:15,680 --> 00:01:17,140
to assassinate the envoy.

22
00:01:29,240 --> 00:01:32,240
The God of War is taking this joke a bit too far.

23
00:01:32,240 --> 00:01:34,080
I, the Minister of Revenue,

24
00:01:34,080 --> 00:01:36,360
who is in charge of the alliance between the two countries,

25
00:01:36,360 --> 00:01:38,039
how could I disregard the law?

26
00:01:38,039 --> 00:01:40,240
Whether you disregarded the law or not,

27
00:01:40,280 --> 00:01:41,960
only His Majesty can decide.

28
00:01:46,039 --> 00:01:49,960
The bead on this folding fan is refined from rock oil.

29
00:01:49,960 --> 00:01:52,080
It is a proof of the diplomatic relations between the two countries.

30
00:01:52,080 --> 00:01:52,800
And it

31
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:55,450
was only given to the Minister of Revenue.

32
00:01:57,360 --> 00:01:58,960
This morning,

33
00:01:58,960 --> 00:02:00,800
I found it at the embassy.

34
00:02:01,080 --> 00:02:02,080
Su Cheng.

35
00:02:02,360 --> 00:02:03,720
What does this mean?

36
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:05,440
I don't need to say more, do I?

37
00:02:05,440 --> 00:02:07,680
I frequently visit the embassy for official business.

38
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:09,340
I accidentally lost the bead.

39
00:02:09,639 --> 00:02:12,680
The God of War has too rich an imagination.

40
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:16,400
The assassination of the envoy

41
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:18,960
I only told the God of War about it.

42
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:21,480
How did you know about it?

43
00:02:21,480 --> 00:02:24,120
I don't know. I accompanied the princess here

44
00:02:24,120 --> 00:02:26,920
and only then learned about the envoy's murder.

45
00:02:26,920 --> 00:02:28,680
The enemy spy has confessed.

46
00:02:29,040 --> 00:02:30,560
He was ordered by you

47
00:02:30,840 --> 00:02:34,200
to assassinate the envoy first and then the princess.

48
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:38,440
Your Majesty.

49
00:02:39,440 --> 00:02:41,970
The evidence against Su Cheng is conclusive.

50
00:02:42,200 --> 00:02:44,960
Please issue an edict to punish him.

51
00:02:46,720 --> 00:02:47,600
Men!

52
00:02:47,600 --> 00:02:48,660
Yes, Your Majesty.

53
00:02:50,240 --> 00:02:52,680
Take Su Cheng to the imperial prison.

54
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:54,160
He will be executed in a few days.

55
00:02:54,160 --> 00:02:54,800
Yes.

56
00:02:58,400 --> 00:03:02,440
This damn shadow knows I can't expose my dual identity.

57
00:03:02,720 --> 00:03:06,320
He actually dared to claim the title of the God of War for himself.

58
00:03:17,200 --> 00:03:18,960
Are you feeling better?

59
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:25,130
The backlash from the pill has passed.

60
00:03:34,600 --> 00:03:35,880
I came too late.

61
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:37,770
I'm sorry you had to suffer.

62
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:43,440
Is Su Cheng really the killer who assassinated the envoy?

63
00:03:44,600 --> 00:03:46,200
The evidence is conclusive.

64
00:03:46,480 --> 00:03:47,880
Who else could it be?

65
00:03:48,720 --> 00:03:50,760
But for someone as cautious as him,

66
00:03:51,040 --> 00:03:53,240
how could he make such a rookie mistake?

67
00:03:54,280 --> 00:03:56,280
I feel something is wrong with this.

68
00:03:56,480 --> 00:03:58,079
It's not like his style.

69
00:03:58,560 --> 00:04:01,290
Have you forgotten how Su Cheng framed us before?

70
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:03,860
As long as he can achieve his goal,

71
00:04:04,560 --> 00:04:06,760
he won't care about the lives of others.

72
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:10,460
But doing this won't fulfill his ambition to restore his country.

73
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:14,730
I feel like he's just taking the opportunity to kick him when he's down.

74
00:04:19,279 --> 00:04:22,010
He who commits many injustices is doomed to fail.

75
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:29,120
Even if Su Cheng is not the real culprit,

76
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:32,159
he can't escape death.

77
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:45,460
Could it be that A-Yu is being used by enemy spies

78
00:04:45,520 --> 00:04:47,380
to intentionally frame Su Cheng?

79
00:04:52,400 --> 00:04:53,400
You may leave now.

80
00:04:53,400 --> 00:04:54,120
Yes.

81
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:57,840
Stop struggling and confess now.

82
00:04:58,280 --> 00:04:59,800
You'll suffer less.

83
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:02,320
You stole my lover,

84
00:05:02,840 --> 00:05:04,680
and my identity.

85
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:08,720
You really are a restless shadow.

86
00:05:10,600 --> 00:05:12,520
If you wear a mask for too long,

87
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:14,360
it becomes hard to take off.

88
00:05:14,640 --> 00:05:15,960
Cut the crap.

89
00:05:17,080 --> 00:05:18,720
I am the God of War now.

90
00:05:18,880 --> 00:05:20,000
The one Ayun loves

91
00:05:20,960 --> 00:05:21,800
is also me.

92
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:23,440
She loves Gu Chengyu.

93
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:26,120
She loves the Gu Chengyu who has been with her for ten years

94
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:28,000
and can protect her.

95
00:05:28,320 --> 00:05:29,480
Not you,

96
00:05:30,360 --> 00:05:32,480
a prisoner whose life is on the line.

97
00:05:36,960 --> 00:05:38,280
What are you laughing at?

98
00:05:38,280 --> 00:05:39,440
I laugh

99
00:05:40,440 --> 00:05:41,800
at you wearing my mask,

100
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:44,600
thinking you could successfully turn the tables.

101
00:05:45,320 --> 00:05:46,400
I laugh

102
00:05:47,560 --> 00:05:50,040
at you being used without even realizing it.

103
00:06:00,720 --> 00:06:02,720
Mo Yu must have been used.

104
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:04,760
Who exactly set this trap?

105
00:06:06,120 --> 00:06:08,580
Someone must have plotted to frame Su Cheng.

106
00:06:20,400 --> 00:06:21,360
Jiuyun,

107
00:06:21,640 --> 00:06:22,720
why are you here?

108
00:06:22,720 --> 00:06:23,760
Let me ask you,

109
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:25,920
who is the assassin behind the attack on the envoy?

110
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:27,080
Stop asking.

111
00:06:27,400 --> 00:06:28,960
For some things,

112
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:31,040
the less you know, the better.

113
00:06:31,880 --> 00:06:33,000
Leave now.

114
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:36,340
I won't leave if you don't tell me.

115
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:38,600
Jiuyun.

116
00:06:56,280 --> 00:06:56,560
Bo Baorui.

117
00:06:56,560 --> 00:06:57,159
Bo Baorui.

118
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:00,970
Zhong Xiaqiang.

119
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:02,130
Peng Yin.

120
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:03,280
Zi Jianqiang Qipin.

121
00:07:03,280 --> 00:07:04,210
Kun Quan Xuhang.

122
00:07:04,840 --> 00:07:05,570
Quan Yulong.

123
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:07,020
Licheng Lefei.

124
00:07:07,440 --> 00:07:07,720
Yunlong Yin Yu Jia Guangjing.

125
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:09,380
Yunlong Yin Yu Jia Guangjing.

126
00:07:11,920 --> 00:07:12,040
Luo Xiaocong Lin Xunbo.
